    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've tried the therapy thing. i've tried the counselors. it's just more of the same cycle. it's like trying to plug holes in a dam that's already collapsed. it's just exhausting. sometimes it feels like there's no actual way out of the loop, just more ways to pretend it's getting better until it isn't.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
